narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The course was fun and interesting. William kept us working hard but also kept class fun.
A fun, intensive course in writing and analyzing.

ENglish 114 is one of the most important classes a freshman should take. Even if you were a good writer in high school, that fact is you probably don't really know how to write at the college/real world level. This class will help you become a real writer. Recommend it to all students.

I would definitely recommend this course to all students, as argumentative writing is a skill that is extremely useful for many other classes as well. I really did enjoy writing the papers, especially the research paper. I feel that I have improved a LOT since the beginning of the semester as a result of the numerous workshops, peer reviews, office hours and just being able to practice consistently. For this section, our class had so much fun watching the South Park episodes. I especially enjoyed the first lesson when we deeply analyzed the revenge quotes taken from Call of Duty.
Fantastic class especially if you are as bad a writer as I am
I would recommend this as an introductory composition course.
